<UserControl xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
             xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
             xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
             mc:Ignorable="d" d:DesignWidth="800" d:DesignHeight="450"
             x:Class="StellarMVVM_2024.Views.finance_institution_archive_screen">
	<UserControl.Styles>
		<StyleInclude Source="/Styles/archive info styles/finance_institution_archive_stylesheet.axaml"/>
	</UserControl.Styles>
	<Panel Background="Pink">
		<StackPanel
		HorizontalAlignment="Center"
		Name="financeInstitutionArchiveStackPanel">
			<TextBlock
				Classes="title"
				PointerReleased="returnPrevious">
				financial institution
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				1. consumers save, spend, borrow, and invest with financial institutions
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				2. a commercial bank accepts deposit from its customers and, in turn, provides loans to its customers
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				3. a credit union is operated on a not-for-profit basis and is owned by its members
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				4. credit unions are similar to a bank in that it accepts deposits and make loans
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				5. there are banks specialized for savings and loans (savings and loans banks)
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				6. securities firms pair people and organizations to invest with investors who need money grow businesses
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				7. people can also use check-cashing stores if they don't have financial institutions
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				8. check-cashing stores and alternatives also provide a faster access to loans
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				9. another alternative are payday loans (however, interest rates are high in repaying the loan)
			</TextBlock>
			<TextBlock
				Classes="infoText">
				10.financial institutions are typically safer than these alternatives
			</TextBlock>
		</StackPanel>

	</Panel>
</UserControl>
